81px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/apple-ios-26-best-features.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/apple-ios-26-best-features.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/apple-ios-26-best-features.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/apple-ios-26-best-features.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"iPhone mockup images showcasing iOS 26 features\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/apple-ios-26-best-features.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/apple-ios-26-best-features.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"other-features\"\u003e\n            Other Features\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSeveral other iOS 26 features will require an iPhone 15 Pro, iPhone 15 Pro Max, or newer. These include automatic order tracking in the Apple Wallet app and the new Genmoji update, which lets you create custom emojis just by typing a description.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"why-every-ios-26-feature-isn-39-t-available-on-all-iphone-models\"\u003e\n                        Why Every iOS 26 Feature Isn\u0026#39;t Available on All iPhone Models\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;Sanuj Bhatia \\/ MakeUseOf\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"iOS 26 Liquid Glass Design on Home screen\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/ios-26-glass-design.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                        \u003cfigcaption\u003eSanuj Bhatia / MakeUseOf\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n                        \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e The reason these features aren\u0026#39;t available on older iPhones comes down to hardware limitations. Many of the new iOS 26 and Apple Intelligence features rely on advanced neural processing, large language models, and machine learning capabilities that are only supported by the latest A-series chips (A17 Pro, A18, and A18 Pro). These chipsets include a powerful Neural Engine capable of handling these tasks efficiently, without slowing down overall performance.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eSince older devices lack the computational power and necessary hardware to run these AI-powered features, Apple has limited them to newer models. Thankfully, Apple will still bring the new design language to all supported iPhones, so even older models can enjoy the fresh UIâ€”though their iOS 26 experience will be more limited. If you don\u0026#39;t care about Apple Intelligence, this might even be a plus.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
